129CharacterSet
130CharacterSetECI::CharsetFromValue(int value)
131{
132 auto it = ECI_VALUE_TO_CHARSET.find(value);
133 if (it != ECI_VALUE_TO_CHARSET.end())
134 {
135 return it->second;
136 }
137 return CharacterSet::Unknown;
138}
